# The mechanism of this repository is the native .cdc under native/.
# GitHub's linguist has no grammar for .cdc, so language statistics cannot
# display it; the attributes below keep the bar from misrepresenting the
# project as a Python/C codebase.

# vendored BiDi micro-bridge (upstream: ETEllis/bidi-coherence-delta-calculus)
runtime/** linguist-vendored

# training harness: support tooling around the native mechanism, not the
# product (trains against native-runtime labels; exports back to .cdc)
torchcdc/** linguist-vendored

*.cdc linguist-detectable
